\id 2JN
\h 2 Yaaya
\toc1 Maktumne ta seeriŋkar taat Yaaya siirtu
\toc2 2 Yaaya
\toc3 2JN
\mt1 2 Yaaya
\mt2 Maktumne ta seeriŋkar taat Yaaya siirtu
\imt1 Pile ka kaawor
\ip Gee kuuk awalle kat kaawe a ŋa Yaaya kat siirit maktumne-an ɗo Egliz rakki. Ŋa kaawaaco maman ŋuu ele ziŋkico. Ele-ak gaara kadar ŋu karmiyaat taat Buŋ kaawtu. Ŋa kaawaaco oki a Iisa, ŋaar gemo ho ŋa Roŋ ka Buŋdi. Ya gem asco ho ŋa beraaco ɓilde kaak arro ar ŋaar-aŋka, ŋuu icenno kaawoy.
\c 1
\s1 Ooy ta awalle
\p 
\v 1 Nun tatkaw ka Eglizdi kat siirke loke, kaŋ taat Buŋ doɓtu iŋ kooginke kuuk nu elgiy min ɗo gelbiner. Kar gay, ŋa nunno di kaak elgiiko, gee okin̰co kuuk ibingit seen sa elgiiko.
\v 2 Ni elgiiko asaan okinte, gi gin seene, ho seen-at goy iŋ ginte elgin iŋ elgina.
\v 3 Tatte Buŋ iŋ Roŋji Iisa Masi yaate barkiyinte. Ŋuur seerco yaate saamiye ho ŋuute oolin̰ aditte. Ampaa ko, ginte kuuk aaɗa seene, gii elguwe ziŋkite.
\s1 Ele ka ziŋkar
\p 
\v 4 Wer galdu dakina, asaan nu dor kadar kooginke daarin̰ aaɗa botol ta seener uudin taat Tatte Buŋ kaawiite.
\v 5 Diŋ gay, gem kol yaaco, ŋu ɗiyaake aman : « Gii elguwe ziŋkite. » Kaaw taar-an, taar marbintoɗo, ta taar di taat gi dortu ɗak ko min ɗo teesindi.
\v 6 Ya gi el ziŋkite, gii gine maan kaak Buŋ kaawtu. Kaaw taar-at ko taat ku dortu min ɗo teesindi.
\s1 Botol ta seener
\p 
\v 7 Nu kaawiiko ansi-aŋ, asaan gay raadiner dakina totir ɗo adiy ka kiɗar. Ŋu ooyɗo kadar Iisa Masi, ŋu weeyig ar ka geemir ho ŋa as ɗo duniiner. Ya gem kaak kaawa ansi-ak, ŋaar adiney ka Iisa Masi ho ŋa jaga gee.
\v 8 Ɗo taar-an, goyoŋ mento, paa kat riy taat ku gintu-an ucaaɗo maala, ho ku asiy gase maan kaak Buŋ ɗiytu a ŋaako bere.
\p 
\v 9 Ibinoŋ kadar ya gem ic kaaw ta Iisa Masi, ho ba aar, ŋa jag min ɗo kaaw-anta ho ŋa jaguma kaawin ku pey, gem-ak kaawco n̰umaaɗo iŋ Buŋ. Kar gay, ya gem kaak icaag kaawin kuuk Iisa ɓilditu gee ho ŋa jagɗo, ŋaar-ak ŋa n̰um iŋ Tatte Buŋ ho iŋ Roŋji oki, kaawco rakki.
\v 10 Iŋ taar-an ko, ya gem ɓaa ɗo werko, kar ŋa ɓilda gee iŋ kaawin kuuk arro ku Iisa Masi, gem ŋaar-ak, dakoŋ obin̰jiɗo geero ho ooy sa, dakon̰ji ooyenno.
\v 11 Ya gem kaak ooyji-ak un̰je ko ziy ɗo gamin kuuk samaanno kuuk gem-ak giniyo.
\s1 Ooy ta ba aaro
\p 
\v 12 Goy gamin dakin kuuk nu rakiiko siire, kar gay, nu rakaaɗo siirin̰ ɗo maktumne-anta. Nu raka ɓaa taliŋko, ansi-ak, gi ɓaayiy kaawe bi iŋ bi. Paa kat, aditte yaa gine portiko.
\v 13 Gem kol booy taat Buŋ doɓtu, koogin ku booke ooyke. Nu ooyko dakina.
